    <title>如何优雅地制作表格</title>
    <link href="https://passing-j.github.io/2017/03/07/dataTables/"/>
    <id>https://passing-j.github.io/2017/03/07/dataTables/</id>
    <published>2017-03-07T07:56:50.414Z</published>
    <updated>2017-03-07T13:26:49.062Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>用简单的方式实现表格布局、从后台获取数据渲染到页面。</p>
<h3 id="需要具备的基础知识"><a href="#需要具备的基础知识" class="headerlink" title="需要具备的基础知识"></a>需要具备的基础知识</h3><p>HTML、CSS、BootStrap、jQuery</p>
<h3 id="用到的主要工具"><a href="#用到的主要工具" class="headerlink" title="用到的主要工具"></a>用到的主要工具</h3><p>jQuery的 <a href="https://datatables.net/" target="_blank" rel="external">DataTables.js</a> 插件</p>
<h3 id="实例1"><a href="#实例1" class="headerlink" title="实例1"></a>实例1</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;!-- 头部引入链接 --&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;link rel=<span class="string">"stylesheet"</span> href=<span class="string">"css/bootstrap.css"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;link rel=<span class="string">"stylesheet"</span> href=<span class="string">"css/plugins/dataTables/datatables.min.css"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;!-- 尾部引入链接 --&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;script src=<span class="string">"js/jquery-2.1.1.js"</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;script src=<span class="string">"js/bootstrap.js"</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;script src=<span class="string">"js/plugins/dataTables/datatables.min.js"</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>  body部分<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;table id=<span class="string">"example"</span> class=<span class="string">"display table table-striped table-bordered table-hover"</span> cellspacing=<span class="string">"0"</span> width=<span class="string">"100%"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;thead&gt;</div><div class="line">        &lt;tr&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Name&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Position&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Office&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Age&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Start date&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Salary&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">        &lt;/tr&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;/thead&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;tfoot&gt;</div><div class="line">        &lt;tr&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Name&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Position&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Office&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Age&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Start date&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Salary&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">        &lt;/tr&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;/tfoot&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;tbody&gt;</div><div class="line">        &lt;tr&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;td&gt;Tiger Nixon&lt;/td&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;td&gt;System Architect&lt;/td&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;td&gt;Edinburgh&lt;/td&gt;</div><div class="line">            ...</div><div class="line">            &lt;td&gt;New York&lt;/td&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;td&gt;27&lt;/td&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;td&gt;2011/01/25&lt;/td&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;td&gt;<span class="variable">$112</span>,000&lt;/td&gt;</div><div class="line">        &lt;/tr&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;/tbody&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;/table&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>js部分<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$(document).ready(<span class="function"><span class="title">function</span></span>() &#123;</div><div class="line">    $(<span class="string">'#example'</span>).DataTable();</div><div class="line">&#125;);</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h3 id="效果图1"><a href="#效果图1" class="headerlink" title="效果图1"></a>效果图1</h3><p><img src="/images/1table/table.jpg" alt="基本效果图" width="80%" align="center"></p>
]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;用简单的方式实现表格布局、从后台获取数据渲染到页面。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;需要具备的基础知识&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#需要具备的基础知识&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;需要具备的基础知识&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;需要具备的基础知识&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;HTML、CSS
    
